com.mesosphere.sdk.config

Interface TaskConfigRouter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultTaskConfigRouter

    public interface TaskConfigRouter
    Interface which maps configuration settings to task types, returning ConfigNamespaces on a per-task-type basis.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Static Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods Default Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      ConfigNamespace getConfig(java.lang.String taskType)
      Returns a ConfigNamespace for all configuration settings to inject into the provided taskType.
      static ConfigNamespace getConfig(TaskConfigRouter router, PodSpec podSpec)
      Convenience method for retrieving a ConfigNamespace against the provided PodSpec's type.

      • getConfig

        ConfigNamespace getConfig(java.lang.String taskType)
        Returns a ConfigNamespace for all configuration settings to inject into the provided taskType. If no matching data was found, returns a new empty ConfigNamespace.
